column5: Fez making ice and so is mother nature....LOL..with these cold temps ice fishing is now becoming a reality...    Fez makes ice at about the 3:50 mark...

"That 70's Show" was one of my favorite sitcom's...and with everyone here asking if the lakes are making ice, I thought of that episode...   ...but you really need to watch the whole 4 minute clip to see why Fez makes ice...
